uk.ac.ebi.gxa.netcdf.generator.service
Class NetCDFGeneratorService<T>

java.lang.Object
  uk.ac.ebi.gxa.netcdf.generator.service.NetCDFGeneratorService<T>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ExperimentNetCDFGeneratorService
public abstract class NetCDFGeneratorService<T>
extends Object

An abstract NetCDFGeneratorService, that provides convenience methods for getting and setting parameters required across all NetCDFGenerator implementations. This class is typed by the type of the repository backing this NetCDFGeneratorService - this may be a file, a datasource, an FTP directory, or something else. Implementing classes have access to this repository and an AtlasDAO that provides interaction with the Atlas database (following an Atlas 2 schema).

All implementing classes should implement the method createNetCDFDocs() which contains the logic for constructing the relevant parts of the index for each implementation. Clients should call generateNetCDFs() to trigger NetCDF construction. At the moment, this method simply delegates to the abstract form, but extra initialisation may go in this method.

Author:
Tony Burdett
